These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-1::.
House: farmhouse, craftsman, cape-cod, ranch-style, futuristic, wooden, townhouse
There 7 different types of food: apricot, pumpkin, pepper, strawberry, artichoke, banana, grapes
 1. the futuristic house is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 2. the person eating apricot is the townhouse house##1
 3. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person eating artichoke is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
 5. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 7. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 8. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
 9. the wooden house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
10. the ranch-style house is the person eating pumpkin##1
11. the ranch-style house is between the person eating pepper and the cape-cod house##2
12. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |   5   |    6     |    7    |
| House   | wooden  | ranch-style | cape-cod  | futuristic | farmhouse | craftsman | townhouse |
| Food           | pepper | pumpkin   | grapes | strawberry  | banana   | artichoke    | apricot    |

