The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daisy, aconite, sunflower, marigold, dahlia, orchid, tulip
 1. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
 2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who growsorchid is in the middle##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
 8. the owner of the hamster is between the person who growsdahlia and the person who growsaconite##2
 9. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
11. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |      4      |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Pet      | hedgehog | hamster | cat   | rat | mouse | pony     | lizard |
| Flower   | aconite     | daisy  | dahlia | orchid     | tulip  | sunflower | marigold |

