 6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
 8. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
