 5. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is writing and the fan of dubstep##2
 9. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of funk##1
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
11. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | folk         | house | pop   | funk        | dubstep  | disco  | techno |
| Hobby         | reading | cooking  | filmmaking | video-games | woodworking | sudoku | writing |

