.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-3-20::.
7 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goat, bird, hamster, ferret, frog, dog
The people have 7 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games, fishing, rock-climbing, writing, card-games, camping
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 6. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is writing and the owner of the ferret##2
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is the owner of the frog##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |    5    |      6       |      7      |
| Pet           | hamster | hedgehog   | ferret | bird    | goat   | dog | frog     |
| Hobby   | camping    | filmmaking | rock-climbing        | board-games | writing | card-games   | fishing |

 